#: Maximum resolution (maxResolution)
msgctxt "#30822"
msgid "Maximum resolution"
msgstr "最大解像度"

msgctxt "#30823"
msgid "Caps video by width; higher-resolution sources are downscaled by the server. No effect when Force direct play is on."
msgstr "動画を幅で制限します。より高い解像度のソースはサーバーによってダウンスケールされます。「ダイレクト再生を強制」が有効な場合は影響しません。"

msgctxt "#30824"
msgid "480p"
msgstr "480p"

msgctxt "#30825"
msgid "720p"
msgstr "720p"

msgctxt "#30826"
msgid "1080p"
msgstr "1080p"

